-- 2024.12.20 - v1.0.1

- feat: Added configuration auto-updater
- feat: Added option to customize the flashlight button
- feat: Added option to hide others' flashlights
- feat: Added `FlashlightDistanceFromBody` to move the light away from the body to avoid casting shadows on the hand
- optimize: Improved duck detection algorithm
- fix: Resolved an issue preventing some users from using the flashlight
